#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/pointclouddatamanagement.rst:87
msgid ""
"Creates a :ref:`virtual point cloud (VPC) <virtual_point_cloud>` from input "
"point cloud data."
msgstr ""
"Erzeugt eine :ref:`virtuelle Punktwolke (VPC) <virtual_point_cloud>` aus den"
" eingegebenen Punktwolkendaten."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/pointclouddatamanagement.rst:89
msgid ""
"If you leave the optional parameters unchecked, the VPC file will be built "
"very quickly as the algorithm will only read metadata of input files. With "
"any of the optional parameters set, the algorithm will read all points which"
" can take some time."
